metadata.description: This 5:1 Edition MixTape Headz NFT is styled after the multi-talented and multi-role music legend Steve Aoki! It features a wardrobe inspired by Steve Aoki's red carpet walk at BRIT Awards 2019 and tape label with his legendary debut studio album "Wonderland". There will be no mistaken identity with this combination!
metadata.name: Steve Aoki: "Wonderland" Edition
